Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: bad-phylo
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Tool for the estimation of the difficulty of phylogenetic placements
Author: Julius Wiegert
Author-email: julius-wiegert@web.de
License-File: LICENSE
Requires-Dist: pandas
Requires-Dist: numpy
Requires-Dist: ete3
Requires-Dist: biopython
Requires-Dist: networkx
Requires-Dist: scipy
Requires-Dist: lightgbm
Requires-Dist: shap
Requires-Dist: rich-argparse
Requires-Dist: pyprobables
Requires-Dist: matplotlib

Bold Assertor of Difficulty (BAD) provides a way to estimate the difficulty of phylogenetic placements. It can help to understand why specific placements are easy or difficult by using Shapley values.
